        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine domini dei aeterni. <persName ref="#people/7"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName> dei nutu <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Si circa loca deo dicata munificenciam nostre+ benignitatis
                        largimur, confidimus hoc ad regnorum statum nostrorum nostraeque animae
                        salutem omnimodo proficere. Idcirco noverit omnium fidelium sanctae dei
                        aecclesiae nostrorumque tam presentium quamque futurorum universitas,
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3960">Azonem</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">ce+nobii</rs> quod <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Casalia #Fisheries #Mills #Allocation_to_churches #Specialized_workers #Ports #Markets #Inquisitio #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Immunity #Fluvial_transport #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1423"><placeName ref="#places/65">Caelum
                                aureum</placeName></orgName> dicitur venerabilem <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbatem</rs> interventu ac petitione <persName ref="#people/1525"
                            key="#Queen #parentOf">Theophanu</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">nostrae dilecte genitricis</rs> et <rs key="#Queen"
                            >consortis regnorum</rs> nostrorum nostram regalem adiisse clementiam,
                        quatinus pro dei amore nostraeque animae remedio predicto caenobio et sibi
                        subvenire et <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">nostra preceptali
                            auctoritate</rs> confirmare et corroborare omnes <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >cortes</rs> et proprietates quas pridem dinoscitur possedisse, et
                        eundem abbatem ex his omnibus investire dignaremur. Cuius petitionibus
                        libentissime aures nostrae pietatis accommodantes nostraeque anime+
                        consulentes pro dei amore predicto ce+nobio atque abbati <rs
                            key="#Allocation_to_churches">concedimus donamus modisque omnibus
                            corroboramus</rs> omnes res et proprietates possessiones omnesque illas
                        cortes quas idem ce+nobium longo tempore visum est possedisse a <persName
                            ref="#people/12">Liudprando</persName> ipsius loci fundatore monachorum
                            <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">donatione</rs> aliorumque hominum oblatione
                        comparatione <rs key="#Commutatio">commutatione</rs> aut quarumcumque
                        legalium conscripcione cartarum concessas, videlicet cortem illam que+
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1492"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Decima"
                                ref="#places/1899">Alpeplana</placeName></geogName> dicitur predicto
                        sancto loco emissam et concessam a quodam <rs key="#Lombard"
                            >Langobardorum</rs> rege <persName key="#Emperor/king #Lombard"
                            ref="#people/344">Ariperto</persName> nomine cunctasque res ad eandem
                        cortem pertinentes vel aspicientes in quibuscumque locis cum territoriis et
                        finibus per preceptum Liudprandi regis per singula loca denuntiatis vel
                        earundem rerum <rs key="#Decima">decimas</rs> que+cumque modo inibi
                        laborate+ fiunt; duas etiam alias corticellas, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1493"><placeName ref="#places/2702"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Maliacem</placeName></geogName> scilicet et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1494"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4381">Caleuadem</placeName></geogName>, et <orgName
                            key="#Chaplain #Churches #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3578"><rs key="#Churches #Chaplain"
                                >capellam</rs> que+ est in honore sanctae dei genitricis Mariae que+
                            dicitur Primasca</orgName>, quae constructa est in <placeName
                            ref="#places/582">valle Bellizona</placeName>, in subsidium et
                        substentationem <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> cum omnibus pertinentiis,
                        cum servis et ancillis atque <rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus</rs> iuste et
                        legaliter eisdem corticellis pertinentibus; aliam quoque cortem que+
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3894"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4382">Uillarasca</placeName></geogName> dicitur et <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansa</rs> que+ in <geogName
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3895">Rouorri</geogName> iacent, et cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3896">Cresiani</geogName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis,
                        cortem insuper quae dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3897"><placeName ref="#places/4385"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Uirgonto</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Casalia #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3898"><rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> sancti
                            Petri</geogName> quod est in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/161"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            Parmensi</geogName>. Concedimus insuper atque delegamus prelibato
                        ce+nobio atque abbati cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/3899"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4904">Pauonem</placeName></geogName> nec non et
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4000"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4386">Ouiliam</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus
                        pertinentiis et adiacentiis suis, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs> aquis aquarumque decursibus <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellis</rs> cultis et incultis rebus servis ancillis
                        aldionibus ubicumque locorum ad easdem cortes pertinentibus, <geogName
                            key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4004"><rs key="#Fisheries">piscariam</rs> vero que+ est in
                                <placeName
                                key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4387">Tauxa</placeName></geogName> et <rs key="#Ports"
                            >portum</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Ports #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4001">Rosiolum</geogName> longo tempore ab ipso monasterio
                        temptum omnemque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> in campania
                            <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/65">Papiensis <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs></placeName>
                        iacentem seque sub terminis continentem. Hac igitur nostri preceptali
                        auctoritate omnes predictas cortes et loca cum rebus et familiis portubus et
                            <rs key="#Markets">mercato</rs> districtionibus molendinis et
                        piscationibus <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque ductibus</rs> cunctisque
                        rebus mobilibus et immobilibus ad iam scriptas cortes et loca in integrum
                        aspicientibus divinorum memores preceptorum iam dicto ce+nobio eiusdemque
                        abbati vel cuicumque pro tempore inibi presidenti confirmamus et
                        corroboramus; omnes insuper illos <rs key="#Specialized_workers"
                            >carpentarios</rs> quos ipse sanctus locus per precepti possidet paginam
                        a tempore antecessoris nostri Liudprandi regis in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Specialized_workers"
                            ref="#places/4388">valle que+ dicitur Antelamo</placeName> vel eos qui
                        sunt in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Specialized_workers"
                            ref="#places/2701">Besozolo</placeName> cum filiis filiabusque
                        agnitioneque cuncta eorum, ut tempore oportuno inibi deserviant ipsi et
                        posteri eorum absque ulla retrectatione perpetualiter; et <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">vada ad piscandum</rs> que+ sunt in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4389">Ticino</placeName>, in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4390">rivo Poloni</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4391">Morasca</placeName> seu <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#estates/4005"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#places/4393">vadum quod dicitur
                            Landemarii</placeName></geogName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4392"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4006">costam Teueredum</geogName></placeName> et aliud
                        quod dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4394"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4007">Sextemascum</geogName></placeName> cum illo
                        medio quod <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4395"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4008">ad Sepem</geogName></placeName> dicitur et illud
                        quod <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4396"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4009">ad Aunella</geogName></placeName> nuncupatur seu
                        etiam illa vada que+ sunt in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4196">Pado</placeName>, habentia priorem terminum a loco
                        qui nuncupatur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4397"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4010">Popula Pagana</geogName></placeName> et
                        pertingentia usque ad locum qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                            ref="#places/4398"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fisheries"
                                ref="#estates/4011">Caput Asi</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Shores">ex utraque parte Padi</rs> cum <rs key="#Islands"
                            >insulis</rs> positis iuxta predictam piscationem vel quicquid ab
                        antiquo tempore per antiquorum regum seu imperatorum donationem optinuit vel
                        Padus invasit aut in futurum irruperit, eidem sancto loco confirmando
                        contradimus. Volumus etiam et concedimus ut <rs key="#Mills">molendina</rs>
                        quae in <placeName
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4900">Catrona</placeName> seu in aliquibus fluminibus
                        predictum monasterium possidet, habeat tam abbas quamque et monachi
                        potestatem levandi atque deponendi, quousque vel quoquo modo eorum
                        decreverit voluntas, et <rs key="#Aqueducts">aque+ductus</rs> qui <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Aqueducts #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/4399">Bauga Liudprandi</placeName> dicebatur, in eorum sit
                        potestate ad irrigandos hortos ipsius monasterii. Sintque omnes res ipsius
                        monasterii, abbas quoque et monachi hominesque libellarii et servi aliaeque
                        omnes res <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">sub nostra imperiali
                            defensione munite+ atque defense</rs>+; et si necessitas fuerit, de
                        rebus ipsius monasterii per <rs key="#Inquisitio">inquisitionem</rs>
                        circumquaque manentium bonorum hominum sicut de nostris imperialibus rebus
                        rei veritas approbetur. Et iuxta definitionem antecessoris nostri <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/12">Liudprandi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">regis</rs> liceat coenobio de propria
                        co[ngr]egatione abbatem eligere, ita ut super eos nulla umquam introducatur
                        persona. Statuimus etiam ut <rs key="#Immunity">nullus rei publice+ minister
                            neque aliquis ex iudiciaria potestate in cunctis predicti monasterii
                            cortibus vel vicis liberos ac servos deinceps inquietare aut ad placitum
                            trahere aut in aliquibus finibus eius placitum tenere aut aliquem
                            pignorare vel detrahere presumat; et quicquid pars publica sperare
                            poterit, eidem monasterio sancto secundum concessionem et confirmationem
                            Liudprandi regis aliorumque regum vel imperatorum sollempni et perpetua
                            stabilitate firmamus</rs>; et quandocumque necessitas imminet, <rs
                            key="#Fluvial_transport">naves</rs> ipsius monasterii per <placeName
                            key="#Teloneum #Immunity" ref="#places/4389">Ticini</placeName> et
                            <placeName key="#Teloneum #Immunity" ref="#places/4196">Padi</placeName>
                        portum quamque per quodlibet aliud discurrat absque alicuius impedimento vel
                            <rs key="#Teloneum">telonei</rs> exactione. Secundum haec etiam regalia
                        scripta sancimus et modis omnibus interdicimus cunctis sub nostra potestate
                        degentibus, ut nullam potestatem deinceps exerceant in predictis rebus a
                        nostra mercede monachis delegatis vel abbatem in aliquo perturbent, sed
                        liceat ipsi abbati suisque successoribus sub regula sancti Benedicti degere
                        et quotidie deo laudes pro animae nostrae remedio regnique nostri statu
                        inibi offerre et omnem congregationem sibi commissam assiduis alimentis
                        pascere et nutrire perpetualiter. Volumus etiam modisque omnibus
                        interdicimus, ut nulla prepotens parvaque persona predictum coenobium
                        proprietario iure aut beneficiali ordine aut preceptali auctoritate nitatur
                        invadere. Precipientes itaque iubemus tam presentibus quamque et futuris, et
                        parti predicti coenobii que+ supra a nobis concessa et confirmata sunt,
                        quolibet tempore nullam presumat inferre molestiam aut contrarietatem, sed
                        sub omni integritate sicuti a nobis concessa sunt, ad utilitatem ipsius
                        monasterii sine aliqua diminoratione permaneant. Si quis igitur aliquando
                        diabolica fraude deceptus contra dei auctoritatem et hanc nostram
                        concessionem et confirmationem aliquid agere temptaverit et iam dictum
                        sanctum locum ex predictis rebus fatigare conatus fuerit, sciat se
                        compositurum auri puri libras mille, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >kamere nostre</rs>+ et medietatem predicti monasterii vel eius abbati.
                        Quod ut verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, manu p[ropria
                        rob]orantes sigilli nostri inpressione inferius iussimus insigniri. Signum
                        domni Ottonis (M.) invictissimi regis. <persName key="#Chancellor"
                            ref="#people/3961">Adelbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Archchancellor" ref="#people/223">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SI. D.) Data nonas
                        aprilis anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCLXXXVIIII, indictione secunda,
                        anno autem tertii Ottonis regnantis VI; actum <placeName ref="#places/4901"
                            >Quitiliniburg</placeName>; feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
